text: Jay Foreman (born 4 October 1984) is an English YouTuber, singer-songwriter and comedian. == Personal life == Foreman was raised in a Jewish household in Stanmore, London. His brother is Darren Foreman, a beatboxer and musician, who is also known as "Beardyman". In June 2019, Foreman and his partner, Jade Nagi, posted about his engagement on Twitter. In August 2021, the couple married at the Fanhams Hall in Ware, Hertfordshire.
